 202:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Include/dsp/fast_math_functions.h ****  /**
 203:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Include/dsp/fast_math_functions.h ****    * @defgroup SQRT Square Root
 204:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Include/dsp/fast_math_functions.h ****    *
 205:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Include/dsp/fast_math_functions.h ****    * Computes the square root of a number.
 206:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Include/dsp/fast_math_functions.h ****    * There are separate functions for Q15, Q31, and floating-point data types.
 207:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Include/dsp/fast_math_functions.h ****    * The square root function is computed using the Newton-Raphson algorithm.
 208:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Include/dsp/fast_math_functions.h ****    * This is an iterative algorithm of the form:
 209:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Include/dsp/fast_math_functions.h ****    * <pre>
 210:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Include/dsp/fast_math_functions.h ****    *      x1 = x0 - f(x0)/f'(x0)
 211:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Include/dsp/fast_math_functions.h ****    * </pre>
 212:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Include/dsp/fast_math_functions.h ****    * where <code>x1</code> is the current estimate,
 213:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Include/dsp/fast_math_functions.h ****    * <code>x0</code> is the previous estimate, and
 214:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Include/dsp/fast_math_functions.h ****    * <code>f'(x0)</code> is the derivative of <code>f()</code> evaluated at <code>x0</code>.
 215:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Include/dsp/fast_math_functions.h ****    * For the square root function, the algorithm reduces to:
 216:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Include/dsp/fast_math_functions.h ****    * <pre>
 217:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Include/dsp/fast_math_functions.h ****    *     x0 = in/2                         [initial guess]
 218:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Include/dsp/fast_math_functions.h ****    *     x1 = 1/2 * ( x0 + in / x0)        [each iteration]
 219:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Include/dsp/fast_math_functions.h ****    * </pre>
 220:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Include/dsp/fast_math_functions.h ****    */
 221:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Include/dsp/fast_math_functions.h **** 
 222:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Include/dsp/fast_math_functions.h **** 
 223:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Include/dsp/fast_math_functions.h ****   /**
 224:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Include/dsp/fast_math_functions.h ****    * @addtogroup SQRT
 225:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Include/dsp/fast_math_functions.h ****    * @{
 226:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Include/dsp/fast_math_functions.h ****    */
 227:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Include/dsp/fast_math_functions.h **** 
 228:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Include/dsp/fast_math_functions.h **** /**
 229:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Include/dsp/fast_math_functions.h ****   @brief         Floating-point square root function.
 230:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Include/dsp/fast_math_functions.h ****   @param[in]     in    input value
 231:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Include/dsp/fast_math_functions.h ****   @param[out]    pOut  square root of input value
 232:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Include/dsp/fast_math_functions.h ****   @return        execution status
 233:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Include/dsp/fast_math_functions.h ****                    - \ref ARM_MATH_SUCCESS        : input value is positive
 234:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Include/dsp/fast_math_functions.h ****                    - \ref ARM_MATH_ARGUMENT_ERROR : input value is negative; *pOut is set to 0
 235:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Include/dsp/fast_math_functions.h ****  */
